snippet: There's no shortage of languages being spoken in the Miami women's locker room these days. Besides English, there can be some Spanish, German, French, a little Danish, even some Dutch dialects....
lead_paragraph: There's no shortage of languages being spoken in the Miami women's locker room these days. Besides English, there can be some Spanish, German, French, a little Danish, even some Dutch dialects.
